title: Travel Backgammon Set—Squaresville
description:
For the discerning gamer on the go, the Travel Backgammon Set is perfect for squaring off in the park, for a weekend getaway, or a match with the neighbor next door. Unique graphic details expertly applied enhance the playing experience. Constructed by hand of FSC certified solid Ash in Los Angeles CA. Includes two sets of checkers and two sets of dice. 10 x 8 x 2 in when traveling, 10 x 16 x 1 in when playing.

  • Dimensions: 10 x 8 x 2 in when traveling, 10 x 16 x 1 in when playing
